Class DefaultConnection<N>

java.lang.Object
squidpony.squidai.astar.DefaultConnection<N>

N - Type of node
All Implemented Interfaces:
Connection<N>
public class DefaultConnection<N>
extends Object
implements Connection<N>
A DefaultConnection is a Connection whose cost is 1. These are often used on a DefaultGraph with Coord as N.
